messages.content:
If you have any questions, Please call Pratheek 
9390674324
And are the opportunities different / exclusive to sucscribers?

Three ways:
1) You can look up lands on the website(1acre.in). It's all free. You can contact the sellers directly. 
2) You can subscribe to 1acre premium (1acre.in/subscribe). You'll get access to MapView plus we'll keep sending good opportunities and will be there, to answer any queries etc. 
3) If your budget is above 5cr and you have an understanding of where you want to pick etc., you can opt for hand-holding, Where we'll assign a person in-house and will actively take care of the requirement.
